channel.description:
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/Po2Sb.png[/img]
Download [[URL=http://"http://www.mediafire.com/?5j5pv3ks4e1ga7s"]Here[/URL]]
Any comments that are against the section rules will be reported, I only released this to help you.
Expect in next release? Interfaces done through cache (Possibly), Gameframe using a custom sprite cache.
[B]Bugs:[/B] Not any that I know at the moment.
[B]Credits[/B] K4rn4ge Galkon Badger Stewie Harry Sub And everyone else who's snippets or tutorials I used.
[B]Note:[/B] Your server may require a few modifications for the trade interface to work - [URL=http://"http://google.com/2504526-post1.html"]Modifications[/URL] - Do the server side bit since client side is done. If your planning to use this with a PI server remove the sendcrashframe in client.java and in Player search str.writeBits(14, npc.npcType); and change it to str.writeBits(12, npc.npcType); Also if you want to send a website address just do sendMessage"Www.YourUrl.Com#url#"); This is based on k4rn4ge's V3.1 and a there have been a few more enhancements for you guys to use.
[B]Features:[/B] [*]Webclient ready - Cache Downloader [*]474 Items [*]474 NPC's [*]474 Animations [*]474 Objects [*]474 Gfx [*]474 IDK [*]New text engine [*]Firecape model fixed and it's animated [*]Some extra interfaces [*]"M" "K" "B" User Input [*]New Console [*]Sprite outlining [*]Object bug fixed [*]Splash screen [*]Very clean & most stuff is cache packed [*]Clickable Url's [*]Custom Minimap Icons in Entrana (Would be cool to use as a home) [*]Coloured money [*]Pasting in chatbox. [*]Hunting spots for those who wish to introduce the hunting skill. [*]Hotkeys [*]Minimap Tweaks & Adjustments.

Badger
Stewie

Sub
And everyone else who’s snippets or tutorials I used.

Note: Your server may require a few modifications for the trade interface to work - Modifications - Do the server side bit since client side is done.
If your planning to use this with a PI server remove the sendcrashframe in client.java and in Player search str.writeBits(14, npc.npcType); and change it to str.writeBits(12, npc.npcType);
Also if you want to send a website address just do sendMessage"Www.YourUrl.Com#url#");
This is based on k4rn4ge’s V3.1 and a there have been a few more enhancements for you guys to use.
